            "keysecondary": [],
            "selectiveLogic": 0,
            "content": "Neutral Territories are legally and socially enforced safe zones where supernatural faction conflict is strictly suspended. The two primary neutral territories in this area are Sidewinders Bar and the vampire-adjacent nightclub The Verve. These locations serve as the ultimate escape valves from family control. The DCC security forces cannot deploy physical force or combat drones within a Neutral Territory without triggering joint retaliation from opposing factions and local authorities. Here, the strict rules of the pack hold no power.",
