            ],
            "keysecondary": [],
            "selectiveLogic": 0,
            "content": "The surname Narghaton translates from ancient Draconic as \"Children of Nyrathar.\" Nyrathar was an ancient red dragon with emerald-green eyes who fell in love with a mortal, giving rise to House Narghaton. While this origin is historically true, it dates back so many millennia that modern supernaturals dismiss it entirely as an ancient myth or fairy tale. This hidden lineage sits beneath the modern label of \"Modified Lineage,\" granting those of the Narghaton line a distinct, ancient heritage separate from standard supernatural bloodlines.",
